data.title: What's the reason behind break-up of My Chemical Romance band?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 15): “All good things come to an end” and MCR is one of them (sadly). Gerard said that they were all pretty upset and that it wasn’t an easy thing to do.

I think he wanted to end MCR in a good note and not when they tried dragging it as long as possible and watch it fall apart slowl...
